{title: Someone Took My Place With You}
{artist: Earl Scruggs and Lester Flatt}
{composer: Written by Lester Flatt, Earl Scruggs, Gurney Thomas}

[G]Now someone took my place with [D7]you
Now you tell me we are [G]through
Someone broke my heart in [D7]two
When they took my place with [G]you
Now [C]someone left me here to [G]cry
And with each day that passes [D7]by
Now [G]I'm found here alone and [D7]blue
Cause someone took my place with [G]you

